{"tid":2212914,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ARM Mac Pro 猜想","createTime":"2020-09-22T07:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T07:44:54.000Z","uid":240069,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"93aa1212c60254905b5e4d762dded5058507647a","tid":2212914,"uid":240069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"APU (CPU + GPU) 就係A14X * 2 MPX module card <br />\n按需求插唔同數量嘅MPX module, 每個module 包含1、2個USB C (TB) interface, 有Infinity Fabric link <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8QSVJd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8QSVJd.png&h=0b42d37f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後升級都唔駁換底板，換(極貴連RAM) MPX module 可上A15, A16 etc <br />\n<br />\n底板就用Apple Designed T3X chip 做system controller 可能built in Thunderbolt 4 controller <br />\nT3X 特別多PCIe lanes <br />\nT3 留俾消費級嘅Mac <br />\n<br />\n目前張MPX afterburner card 同Radeon VII 可以照用返 (driver support Radeon VII and RDNA2)"},{"pid":"b60a44bad90e3b410acdbc646e8f99475d909379","tid":2212914,"uid":37136,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"apple會咁好死比你換<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"32e1617aac51e3041d9c45d238b66c08f82ca4da","tid":2212914,"uid":52068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b60a44bad90e3b410acdbc646e8f99475d909379","tid":2212914,"uid":37136,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"apple會咁好死比你換<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:12:49.000Z","msg":"落拉爆螺絲 aa膠再燒焊"},{"pid":"eddfb54a737fcf58e3892e36f74340f7dcdb2faf","tid":2212914,"uid":240069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b60a44bad90e3b410acdbc646e8f99475d909379","tid":2212914,"uid":37136,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"apple會咁好死比你換<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"c